description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for an opportunity to provide experience in Acute Medicine and Elderly Care?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Hampshire Hospitals we are looking to fill a split position starting now until early August 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Acute Medicine: &lt;span&gt;Working in the Ambulatory Care and Acute Assessment unit, providing you with a wide breadth of acute medicine experience in these consultant led areas. This post provides an excellent opportunity to strengthen your clinical acumen, diagnostic and practical skills in acute medicine, with real time consultant feedback and supervision. The department has a strong sense of teamwork, pride and provides opportunities for professional development.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Elderly care: This area will develop your skills in acute frailty, geriatric ward medicine and community care for our elderly population. There is opportunity for specialist clinics and Emergency department in reach. Acute frailty services are in development at the trust and there is opportunity to contribute to this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Tanju Lad - Consultant Acute Medicine&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E-mail: Tanuj.Lad@hhft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
